Overview

Demonstrates replay and recovery behavior within the HyperSync Lender Operating System following a controlled processing interruption.

The recording validates replay governance, recovery controls, operational resiliency, and successful restoration of borrower processing.

Recording Objectives

Demonstrate:

Borrower processing

Controlled failure

Replay queue population

Replay execution

Recovery success

Audit updates

Final completion
Recording Scenario

Example:

Borrower passes validation

Controlled interruption occurs

Outbound processing stops

Replay queue populated

Replay succeeds

Borrower processing completed
Recording Flow
Section 1

Lender Intake

Show:

Borrower intake

Loan type tagging

Governance updates
Section 2

Lender Process

Show:

Validation pass

Routing completion

PRC governance updates
Section 3

Controlled Failure

Show:

Outbound interruption

Failure state

Replay eligibility

Demonstrate:

Processing interruption

Failure recorded

Recovery path initiated
Section 4

Replay Governance

Show:

Replay Queue

Attempt Count

Replay Status

Recovery execution
Section 5

Recovery Completion

Show:

CRM Sync completion

Assignment completion

Audit updates

Final completed state
Success Criteria

Visible evidence of:

Lend_App_ID continuity

Correlation_ID continuity

